9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"The Windmill | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"In the last years of the Ottoman Empire, a poor little Anatolian town named Saripinar is hit by a minor earthquake which has neither destroyed nor left it with many casualties. However, a telegraph sent to the central government exaggerates the situation and mentions that the governor of the town has been severely wounded, making the event a nationwide matter."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148394/the-windmill"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"The Windmill"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"In the last years of the Ottoman Empire, a poor little Anatolian town named Saripinar is hit by a minor earthquake which has neither destroyed nor left it with many casualties. However, a telegraph sent to the central government exaggerates the situation and mentions that the governor of the town has been severely wounded, making the event a nationwide matter."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148394/the-windmill"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/4N3qikpEcTBLooR86hx6PAfMLmX.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"The Windmill"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"In the last years of the Ottoman Empire, a poor little Anatolian town named Saripinar is hit by a minor earthquake which has neither destroyed nor left it with many casualties. However, a telegraph sent to the central government exaggerates th